#: ../../agent_skills.rst:2
msgid "Agent Skills（智能体技能）"
msgstr "Agent Skills"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:5
msgid "概述"
msgstr "Overview"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:7
msgid ""
"Agent Skills 是 ``PersonAgent`` 的能力组织方式。``PersonAgent`` 是一个轻量的 ReAct "
"编排器，其能力 由**可插拔的 Skill 流水线**提供。它解决的问题不只是“如何写插件”，而是如何把社会科学中的行为机制拆 "
"成可以检查的仿真环节：一个人看到了什么，如何解释这个情境，形成了什么意图，采取了什么行动，又把哪些 经历带到后续决策中。"
msgstr ""
"Agent Skills are the capability organization mechanism for "
"``PersonAgent``. The problem it solves goes beyond \"how to write "
"plugins\" — it addresses how to decompose behavioral mechanisms from "
"social science into inspectable simulation stages: what a person "
"perceives, how they interpret the situation, what intention they form, "
"what action they take, and which experiences they carry into subsequent "
"decisions."

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:12
msgid "Skill 遵循 **metadata-first、selected-only** 模型："
msgstr "Skills follow a **metadata-first, selected-only** model:"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:14
msgid "**选择阶段**：LLM 只看到 Skill 目录（``name`` + ``description``），据此决定激活哪些。"
msgstr ""
"**Selection stage**: the LLM only sees the skill catalog (``name`` + "
"``description``) and decides which skills to activate from that metadata."

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:15
msgid "**执行阶段**：只有被 LLM 选中的 Skill 才会被加载、读取、执行（惰性加载）。"
msgstr ""
"**Execution stage**: only skills selected by the LLM are loaded, read, and executed "
"(lazy loading)."

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:17
msgid ""
"好处是提示词体积可控（未选中的 Skill 不进上下文），且 Skill 可独立演进、热加载。一个 Skill 是一个 自包含目录，至少含一个 "
"``SKILL.md``，包含 YAML frontmatter 和行为文档；可选地含 ``scripts/`` 可执行脚本和 "
"``references/`` 参考资料。"
msgstr ""
"This keeps prompt size under control because unselected skills do not "
"enter the context, while skills can evolve independently and be hot-"
"loaded. A skill is a self-contained directory with at least one "
"``SKILL.md`` file (YAML frontmatter plus behavior documentation), and "
"optionally ``scripts/`` for executable scripts and ``references/`` for "
"reference material."

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:23
msgid ""
"本页描述的是 **Ray 重构后** 的技能子系统。旧的内置 ``observation`` / ``cognition`` / ``plan``"
" / ``memory`` 四技能已被移除；技能基础设施（registry / runtime）从 ``agent/skills/`` 下沉到 "
":mod:`agentsociety2.agent.base`；Skill 脚本默认在 agent 进程内经 ``entrypoint`` "
"执行，而不再是 每步 fork 子进程。当前唯一内置技能是 :ref:`daily-guidance`。最权威的工程说明见源码 "
"``agentsociety2/agent/skills/README.md``。"
msgstr ""
"This page describes the **post-Ray-refactor** skill subsystem. The old "
"built-in ``observation`` / ``cognition`` / ``plan`` / ``memory`` skills "
"have been removed; skill infrastructure (registry / runtime) has moved "
"from ``agent/skills/`` down into :mod:`agentsociety2.agent.base`; and "
"skill scripts now execute by default in the agent process through "
"``entrypoint`` instead of forking a subprocess on every step. The only "
"current built-in skill is :ref:`daily-guidance`. The most authoritative "
"engineering notes are in the source file "
"``agentsociety2/agent/skills/README.md``."

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:31
msgid "设计目标"
msgstr "Design Goals"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:33
msgid "**按需加载**：降低每步不必要的上下文占用与执行开销。"
msgstr ""
"**On-demand loading**: Reduces unnecessary context usage and execution "
"overhead at each step."

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:34
msgid "**可解释选择**：选择依据来自 catalog 中的简短描述，便于调试和复盘。"
msgstr ""
"**Interpretable selection**: Selection is based on short descriptions in "
"the catalog, facilitating debugging and review."

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:35
msgid "**热更新友好**：支持运行时扫描、激活/停用与重载（自定义 skill 放进 ``custom/skills/`` 即被发现）。"
msgstr ""
"**Hot-update friendly**: supports runtime scanning, "
"activation/deactivation, and reloading; custom skills are discovered when"
" placed under ``custom/skills/``."

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:36
msgid "**文件约定解耦**：技能通过 workspace 文件交换状态，而不是互相直接调用。"
msgstr ""
"**File-convention decoupling**: Skills exchange state through workspace "
"files rather than calling each other directly."

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:37
msgid "**进程内执行**：脚本默认走 ``entrypoint``，复用热解释器，毫秒级、完全并发安全。"
msgstr ""
"**In-process execution**: scripts use ``entrypoint`` by default, reuse a "
"warm interpreter, run in milliseconds, and are fully concurrency-safe."

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:41
msgid "Skill 目录结构"
msgstr "Skill Directory Structure"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:43
msgid ""
"内置技能位于 ``agentsociety2/agent/skills/``，自定义技能位于工作区 "
"``custom/skills/``，环境模块技能 由环境提供。``SkillRegistry`` 按目录扫描，用 "
"``namespace@name`` 作为稳定 ``skill_id``。"
msgstr ""
"Built-in skills live under ``agentsociety2/agent/skills/``; custom skills"
" live under workspace ``custom/skills/``; environment-module skills are "
"provided by the environment. ``SkillRegistry`` scans directories and uses"
" ``namespace@name`` as the stable ``skill_id``."

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:68
msgid ""
"扫描规则：每个子目录必须含 ``SKILL.md``，否则跳过；以 ``.`` 或 ``_`` 开头的目录被忽略；同名（同 "
"``skill_id``）先到先得。agent 启动时通过 ``default_activated_skill_ids`` 配置默认激活哪些 "
"skill。"
msgstr ""
"Scan rules: each subdirectory must contain ``SKILL.md`` or it is skipped;"
" directories starting with ``.`` or ``_`` are ignored; duplicate names "
"(same ``skill_id``) are first-wins. At agent startup, "
"``default_activated_skill_ids`` configures which skills are activated by "
"default."

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:73
msgid "SKILL.md 格式"
msgstr "SKILL.md Format"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:75
msgid "每个 skill 目录必须含 ``SKILL.md``，头部用 YAML frontmatter 描述元数据："
msgstr ""
"Each skill directory must contain a ``SKILL.md`` file. The file header "
"uses YAML frontmatter to describe metadata:"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:91
msgid "frontmatter 字段："
msgstr "Frontmatter fields:"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:97 ../../agent_skills.rst:187
msgid "字段"
msgstr "Field"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:98 ../../agent_skills.rst:188
#: ../../agent_skills.rst:294
msgid "说明"
msgstr "Description"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:99
msgid "``name``"
msgstr "``name``"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:100
msgid "显示名，与命名空间组合成 ``skill_id``（``namespace@name``）。"
msgstr ""
"Display name, combined with the namespace to form ``skill_id`` "
"(``namespace@name``)."

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:101
msgid "``description``"
msgstr "``description``"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:102
msgid "**目录描述**——选择阶段 LLM 唯一可见的文本，决定是否激活。务必精炼、可操作。"
msgstr ""
"**Catalog description**: the only text visible to the LLM during "
"selection, and what determines whether it activates the skill. Keep it "
"concise and actionable."

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:103
msgid "``script``"
msgstr "``script``"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:104
msgid "可选，默认脚本相对路径（如 ``scripts/daily_guidance.py``）。"
msgstr ""
"Optional default script relative path, such as "
"``scripts/daily_guidance.py``."

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:105
msgid "``hooks``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:106
msgid "可选，生命周期 hook 脚本映射，键为 hook 类型（``pre_step`` / ``post_step``），值为相对脚本路径。"
msgstr ""
"Optional lifecycle hook script mapping. Keys are hook types (``pre_step`` / "
"``post_step``), and values are relative script paths."

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:110
msgid ""
"frontmatter 之后的 Markdown 正文，是 skill 被 **激活后** 注入 system prompt 的行为说明。未激活时"
" 不进上下文。激活时支持 ``$ARGUMENTS`` / ``$1`` / ``$2`` 占位符替换与 ``!cmd`` 命令输出注入。"
msgstr ""
"The Markdown body after the frontmatter is the behavior instruction "
"injected into the system prompt **after the skill is activated**. It does"
" not enter context when inactive. When activated, it supports "
"``$ARGUMENTS`` / ``$1`` / ``$2`` placeholder substitution and ``!cmd``"
" command-output injection."

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:115
msgid "可见性与激活"
msgstr "Visibility and Activation"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:117
msgid "**可见（visible）**：skill 出现在目录里，LLM 能看到、能选择激活。"
msgstr ""
"**Visible**: the skill appears in the catalog, so the LLM can see it and "
"choose to activate it."

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:118
msgid ""
"**激活（activated）**：skill 的 ``SKILL.md`` 正文被注入 system prompt，其脚本 / hook "
"可被调用。"
msgstr ""
"**Activated**: the body of the skill's ``SKILL.md`` is injected into the "
"system prompt, and its scripts / hooks can be called."

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:120
msgid "LLM 通过下列工具操作 skill："
msgstr "The LLM operates on skills through these tools:"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:126
msgid "工具"
msgstr "Tool"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:127
msgid "作用"
msgstr "Purpose"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:128
msgid "``activate_skill``"
msgstr "``scripts/hello_skill.py``:"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:129
msgid "加载某 skill 的 ``SKILL.md`` 进上下文。"
msgstr "Load a skill's ``SKILL.md`` into context."

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:130
msgid "``deactivate_skill``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:131
msgid "从上下文移除某 skill。"
msgstr "Remove a skill from context."

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:132
msgid "``read_skill_file``"
msgstr "``reload_skill(name)``"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:133
msgid "读取 skill 内文件（渐进式披露）。"
msgstr "Read files inside a skill for progressive disclosure."

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:134
msgid "``execute_skill_script``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:135
msgid "执行 skill 脚本。"
msgstr "Execute a skill script."

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:137
msgid "ReAct 主循环每个 ``step()`` 开始前会刷新可见 skill 集合；``ask`` 模式（外部问答）下只暴露只读工具子集。"
msgstr ""
"Before each ``step()``, the main ReAct loop refreshes the visible skill "
"set. In ``ask`` mode for external Q&A, only the read-only tool subset is "
"exposed."

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:141
msgid "脚本执行模型（进程内 entrypoint）⭐"
msgstr "Script Execution Model: In-Process entrypoint"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:143
msgid ""
"这是当前实现的**核心**。历史上 skill 脚本以子进程方式执行（``python script.py <argv>``），每个 agent "
"每步都 fork 一个新解释器，冷启动开销巨大。改版后 skill 脚本默认**在 agent 进程内执行**，分三档优先级："
msgstr ""
"This is the **core** of the current implementation. Historically, skill "
"scripts executed as subprocesses (``python script.py <argv>``), forking a"
" new interpreter for every agent on every step, with high cold-start "
"cost. After the redesign, skill scripts execute **inside the agent "
"process** by default, with three priority levels:"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:153
msgid "entrypoint 契约（推荐所有 skill 脚本遵循）"
msgstr "entrypoint Contract: Recommended for All Skill Scripts"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:155
msgid "Skill 脚本可在模块顶层定义一个 ``entrypoint``，runtime 会优先调用它："
msgstr ""
"A skill script can define an ``entrypoint`` at module top level; the "
"runtime calls it first:"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:169
msgid "要点："
msgstr "Key points:"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:171
msgid ""
"**签名兼容**：runtime 检测形参数量，``entrypoint(argv)`` 与 ``entrypoint(argv, ctx)`` "
"都支持， **强烈建议接受 ``ctx``**。"
msgstr ""
"**Signature compatibility**: the runtime detects arity, supporting both "
"``entrypoint(argv)`` and ``entrypoint(argv, ctx)``. **Accepting ``ctx`` "
"is strongly recommended**."

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:173
msgid "**返回 stdout**：不要依赖 ``print`` 被 capture；直接 ``return`` 结果字符串。"
msgstr ""
"**Return stdout**: do not rely on captured ``print`` output; directly "
"``return`` the result string."

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:174
msgid ""
"**异常即失败**：``entrypoint`` 抛异常 → 记为失败（``exit_code=1``）。不要用 "
"``sys.exit()``；逻辑 失败在返回文本里写 ``ok: false``。"
msgstr ""
"**Exceptions mean failure**: if ``entrypoint`` raises, the call is "
"recorded as failed (``exit_code=1``). Do not use ``sys.exit()``; "
"represent logical failure in the returned text, for example ``ok: "
"false``."

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:176
msgid "**幂等加载**：runtime 按 ``(路径, mtime)`` 缓存模块，模块顶层代码只执行一次。"
msgstr ""
"**Idempotent loading**: the runtime caches modules by ``(path, mtime)``, "
"so module top-level code executes only once."

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:179
msgid "SkillScriptContext"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:181
msgid "进程内执行时上下文通过 ``ctx`` 显式传入（定义在 ``agent/base/runtime.py``）："
msgstr ""
"For in-process execution, context is passed explicitly through ``ctx`` "
"(defined in ``agent/base/runtime.py``):"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:189
msgid "``ctx.workspace_root``"
msgstr "``workspace_root()``"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:190
msgid "本 agent 的工作区根目录（子进程时代对应环境变量 ``AGENT_WORK_DIR``）。"
msgstr ""
"Workspace root for this agent, corresponding to the old subprocess-era "
"``AGENT_WORK_DIR`` environment variable."

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:191
msgid "``ctx.skill_dir``"
msgstr "``SKILL.md``:"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:192
msgid "本 skill 的包根目录。"
msgstr "Skill Directory Structure"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:193
msgid "``ctx.skill_id`` / ``ctx.skill_name``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:194
msgid "注册 id（``namespace@name``）/ 显示名。"
msgstr "Registered id (``namespace@name``) / display name."

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:195
msgid "``ctx.env``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:196
msgid "子进程方式本会设置的 env 快照（dict）。"
msgstr "Environment snapshot (dict) that would have been set in subprocess mode."

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:199
msgid "并发安全要求（重要）"
msgstr "Concurrency Safety Requirements (Important)"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:201
msgid ""
"一次模拟里多个 agent 在**同一个进程**内并发跑各自的 skill 脚本。下列进程级状态是**共享**的，绝不能在 entrypoint "
"里直接读写，否则产生数据竞争："
msgstr ""
"In one simulation, multiple agents may run their skill scripts "
"concurrently **inside the same process**. The following process-level "
"state is **shared** and must not be read or written directly inside "
"``entrypoint`` or data races can occur:"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:208
msgid "❌ 禁止"
msgstr "Do not"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:209
msgid "✅ 替代方案"
msgstr "Use instead"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:210
msgid "``os.environ[\"AGENT_WORK_DIR\"] = ...``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:211
msgid "用 ``ctx.workspace_root``"
msgstr "``workspace_root()``"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:212
msgid "``os.chdir(workspace)``"
msgstr "``workspace_root()``"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:213
msgid "用绝对路径（``ctx.workspace_root / ...``）"
msgstr "``workspace_root()``"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:214
msgid "``print(...)`` 并依赖 stdout 捕获"
msgstr "``print(...)`` while relying on stdout capture"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:215
msgid "在 entrypoint 里 ``return`` 字符串"
msgstr "``return`` a string from ``entrypoint``"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:216
msgid "模块级可变全局当作“本次调用状态”"
msgstr "Using mutable module-level globals as per-call state"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:217
msgid "用 ``contextvars.ContextVar`` （任务级隔离）"
msgstr "Use ``contextvars.ContextVar`` for task-level isolation"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:220
msgid "动态包装器"
msgstr "Dynamic Wrapper"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:222
msgid ""
"无 ``entrypoint`` 的脚本由动态包装器就地执行：以 ``__name__ == \"__main__\"`` 在全新命名空间 "
"``exec`` 脚本源码——语义等价子进程，但复用热解释器、无 fork。由于临时设置 ``os.environ`` / "
"``os.chdir`` / 捕获 stdout 这些进程级状态，动态包装器由一把全局锁 **串行** 执行。因此推荐所有热路径脚本提供 "
"``entrypoint``，享受完全并发。"
msgstr ""
"Scripts without ``entrypoint`` are executed in-place by a dynamic "
"wrapper: the source is ``exec``-ed in a fresh namespace with ``__name__ "
"== \"__main__\"``. This is semantically equivalent to a subprocess, but "
"reuses the warm interpreter and avoids fork. Because it temporarily "
"mutates process-level state such as ``os.environ``, ``os.chdir``, and "
"stdout capture, the dynamic wrapper runs **serially** behind a global "
"lock. Therefore, all hot-path scripts should provide ``entrypoint`` for "
"full concurrency."

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:230
msgid "内置技能：daily-guidance"
msgstr "Built-in Skill: daily-guidance"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:232
msgid ""
"当前唯一内置技能是 ``daily-guidance``（``built-in@daily-"
"guidance``），面向**时间尺度在小时及以下**的 日常行为模拟。它让 agent 先形成一天的完整 "
"Story（``state/daily_guidance/YYYY-MM-DD/story.yaml``）， 再按 Story "
"指导每个仿真步的行为："
msgstr ""
"The only current built-in skill is ``daily-guidance`` (``built-in@daily-"
"guidance``), designed for daily behavior simulation at hourly and sub-"
"hourly time scales. It has the agent first form a complete Story for the "
"day (``state/daily_guidance/YYYY-MM-DD/story.yaml``), then uses that "
"Story to guide behavior on each simulation step:"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:236
msgid "**用 ``plan --json`` 提交一天的安排**：脚本校验后写入 story.yaml。"
msgstr ""
"**Submit the day plan with ``plan --json``**: the script validates it and"
" writes ``story.yaml``."

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:237
msgid ""
"**执行状态由时钟推导**：``completed_segments`` / ``current_segment_id`` 是 "
"``(segments, 当前仿真时间)`` 的函数，由脚本在读取时计算。"
msgstr ""
"**Execution state is derived from the clock**: ``completed_segments`` / "
"``current_segment_id`` are functions of ``(segments, current simulation "
"time)`` and are computed by the script when read."

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:239
msgid ""
"**``pre_step`` hook 每步注入当前 segment**：含 ``activity`` 和 "
"``location_policy``，agent 据此移动与 回答问卷。"
msgstr ""
"**The ``pre_step`` hook injects the current segment on every step**: it "
"includes ``activity`` and ``location_policy``, which the agent uses for "
"movement and questionnaire answers."

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:241
msgid "内含 needs-decay 模型与 story revision 能力，用于评估和修正每日安排。"
msgstr ""
"It includes a needs-decay model and story revision capability for "
"evaluating and correcting daily schedules."

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:243
msgid ""
"daily-mobility 等实验默认激活该 skill。它也是“进程内 entrypoint + pre_step hook 注入”的参考实现"
" （见 ``agent/skills/daily-guidance/scripts/daily_guidance.py``）。"
msgstr ""
"Experiments such as daily-mobility activate this skill by default. It is "
"also the reference implementation for in-process ``entrypoint`` plus "
"``pre_step`` hook injection (see ``agent/skills/daily-"
"guidance/scripts/daily_guidance.py``)."

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:246
msgid ""
"旧的 ``observation`` / ``cognition`` / ``plan`` / ``memory`` "
"四技能已被移除；这些认知/行为能力现在通过 自定义 skill + workspace 状态文件 + ``ask_env`` 组合实现。"
msgstr ""
"The old ``observation`` / ``cognition`` / ``plan`` / ``memory`` skills "
"have been removed. Those cognitive and behavioral capabilities are now "
"implemented through custom skills, workspace state files, and "
"``ask_env``."

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:251
msgid "生命周期 Hook（pre_step / post_step）"
msgstr "Lifecycle Hooks: pre_step / post_step"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:253
msgid "在 ``SKILL.md`` 的 ``hooks:`` 里声明，每个仿真步自动触发："
msgstr ""
"Declare hooks under ``hooks:`` in ``SKILL.md``. They run automatically on"
" every simulation step:"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:255
msgid ""
"``pre_step``：``agent.step()`` 开头、ReAct 循环之前运行。典型用途：根据仿真时钟推导当前状态， "
"**注入到首轮上下文**。"
msgstr ""
"``pre_step``: runs at the start of ``agent.step()``, before the ReAct "
"loop. Typical use: derive current state from the simulation clock and "
"**inject it into the first-turn context**."

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:257
msgid "``post_step``：ReAct 循环之后运行。典型用途：记录实际行为、收尾。"
msgstr ""
"``post_step``: runs after the ReAct loop. Typical use: record actual "
"behavior and perform cleanup."

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:259
msgid ""
"hook 以 ``--args-json`` 形式接收 payload（含 ``hook_type`` / ``tick`` / ``time``"
" / ``agent_id`` / ``step_count``）。**改版后**，``pre_step`` 的输出渲染为**专用的 "
"``<skill_hooks>`` XML 分块**，出现在 ReAct 首条 user 消息中——而不是被塞进通用 observation "
"dump（那容易被 LLM 忽略）。例如："
msgstr ""
"Hooks receive their payload through ``--args-json`` (including "
"``hook_type`` / ``tick`` / ``time`` / ``agent_id`` / ``step_count``). "
"**After the redesign**, ``pre_step`` output is rendered as a **dedicated "
"``<skill_hooks>`` XML block** in the first ReAct user message, rather "
"than being buried in a generic observation dump that the LLM can easily "
"ignore. For example:"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:272
msgid "这样 agent 不必再花一轮观察去“重新发现”状态。"
msgstr ""
"This prevents the agent from spending another observation round to "
"rediscover its state."

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:276
msgid "环境类 Skill（``env:`` 前缀）"
msgstr "Environment Skills: ``env:`` Prefix"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:278
msgid ""
"以 ``env:`` 开头的 ``skill_id`` 会被 ``execute_skill_script`` 重定向到 "
"``ask_env``（走环境路由 ``RouterBase``），而非执行脚本。用于把“查询/操作仿真环境”包装成 skill 暴露给 "
"LLM。这类 skill 不需要 ``entrypoint``。"
msgstr ""
"A ``skill_id`` starting with ``env:`` is **redirected to ``ask_env``** by"
" ``execute_skill_script`` and goes through the environment router "
"(``RouterBase``) instead of executing a script. This wraps querying or "
"operating on the simulation environment as a skill exposed to the LLM. "
"These skills do not need ``entrypoint``."

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:284
msgid "SkillRegistry API"
msgstr "SkillRegistry API"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:286
msgid ""
"``SkillRegistry`` 是技能的发现中心（位于 "
":mod:`agentsociety2.agent.base.registry`）。在大规模仿真下 它是共享只读单例（不再每 agent 复制）。"
msgstr ""
"``SkillRegistry`` is the skill discovery center, located in "
":mod:`agentsociety2.agent.base.registry`. In large-scale simulations it "
"is a shared read-only singleton, no longer copied per agent."

